tion":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event68-05-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"아, 아야 짱이 새로운 사진을 올린 것 같아.\n어디~ 「수제 초콜릿 준비 개시」라고 썼는데……\n……엥? 어째서 린코 짱이랑 같이 뜨개질을 하는 거지?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event68-05-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"아니지, 이런 걸 보고 있을 때가 아니잖아.\n히마리 짱의 페이지는…… 어디.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event68-05-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"(이거야……)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event68-05-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"(응? 이 사진은…… 서점에서 찍은 거려나?\n여기 찍힌 건…… 아르바이트 정보지, 맞지?)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event68-05-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"내용은……\n「용돈이 대대대위기!!」……라니.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event68-05-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"아, 카논 씨, 죄송해요.\n그래서 아까 이야기를 계속해주셨으면 하는데……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event68-05-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"그, 그전에 잠깐 이것 좀 봐줘.\n히마리 짱의 SNS 페이지인데……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event68-05-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"……네?\n이건 설마 아르바이트를 찾고 있는 건가요?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event68-05-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"나도 잘 모르겠지만……\n아마 그런 의미겠지?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event68-05-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"응?\n여기 찍혀 있는 서점은 상점가에 있는 서점이에요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event68-05-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"방금 사진을 올린 참이니까, 아직 가게에 있을지도 몰라요.\n히마리 짱이 신경 쓰이는데 가게 일도 있고, 어떡하죠.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event68-05-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"그거라면 내가 갔다 올게.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event68-05-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"네? 괜찮겠어요?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event68-05-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"응, 물론.\n어제 히마리 짱이 상담을 할 때 내가 제대로 해줬으면\n이런 일은 없었을 것 같으니까.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event68-05-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"카논 씨……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event68-05-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"괜찮아, 나한테 맡겨.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event68-05-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"네, 부탁드릴게요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event68-05-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"갔다 올게!\n……그런데, 그러니까, 서점이 어디에 있는 거야?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event68-05-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"히마리","body":"정말, 사아야! 평~~생의 소원이야!\n아르바이트를 뽑는 가게를 소개해주기만 하면 된다니까!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event68-05-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"사아야","body":"것보다, 진심이야?\n그만두는 게 좋다니까.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"event68-05-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseW